                <h1>Beyond the arc: Duke demolishes Kentucky in season opener</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/242b28fc-7ccb-4d61-8405-e94c4a5c464b.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;RJ&#x20;Barrett&#x27;s&#x20;33&#x20;points&#x20;broke&#x20;the&#x20;Duke&#x20;record&#x20;for&#x20;most&#x20;points&#x20;scored&#x20;in&#x20;a&#x20;freshman&#x27;s&#x20;college&#x20;debut.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>RJ Barrett's 33 points broke the Duke record for most points scored in a freshman's college debut.</p>

